net.hudup.listener

Class RemoteInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hudup.listener.RemoteInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, TextParsable

    public class RemoteInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, Cloneable, TextParsable
    This class called remote information contains information of remote server or service. In current implementation, it contains host and port of the remote server (service) and account name / password to access such server (service).
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
    See Also:
